{"tid":444693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警回家探母遇襲 遭鄰居劏肚命危","createTime":"2017-10-22T16:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T18:19:27.000Z","uid":1749,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"476760264a6e99789d92be89b48fab0cc2c81197","tid":444693,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:43:16.000Z","msg":"葵涌發生休班警遇襲案，周日(22日)晚9時許，一名40歲休班警員到安蔭邨豐蔭樓探望母親，其間於走廊時，遭52歲姓楊男子持摺刀襲擊，他走避不及身中多刀，包括胸及腹。現場消息稱，其中一刀將腹部劏開，部份腸臟溢出，他事後由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院搶救。遇襲警員隸屬西九龍交通意外特別調查隊，現時情況危殆，留醫深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n警方於現場拘捕涉傷人的姓楊男子，初步懷疑他患有精神病，事後亦須送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171022&amp;guid=57365140&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171022%26guid%3D57365140%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=ZNUdvFdjIg9Wu8ZJmuaNlWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7af49fb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171022%26guid%3D57365140%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=bc0b87ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171022&amp;guid=57365140&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n香港地真係多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd7a4272b2991bf502b4d709ba1a208b7975036","tid":444693,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:45:06.000Z","msg":"好似係第三個同類 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再 post 多次：<br />\n其實精神病人／白卡人士都應該要負刑事責任，如果唔係，拉咗但冇事放返出嚟，下個中招嘅，可能我或者你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外葵涌有葵涌醫院收精神病人，呢一帶嘅公屋相信都住咗唔少院友，方便佢哋覆診，某程度上係高危地帶<br />\n<br />\n（不過當然精神病有好多種分類，未必種種都係會殺人）<br />\n<br />\n近排好似多咗好多呢啲癡線佬新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港發生咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c